#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.fft.hfft.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.fft.hfft"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.hfft.hfft:1 of
msgid ""
"Compute the FFT of a signal that has Hermitian symmetry, i.e., a real "
"spectrum."
msgstr "计算具有 Hermitian 对称性（即实数谱）信号的 FFT。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.hfft.hfft of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.hfft.hfft:4 of
msgid "The input tensor."
msgstr "输入张量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.hfft.hfft:6 of
msgid ""
"Length of the transformed axis of the output. For `n` output points, "
"``n//2 + 1`` input points are necessary.  If the input is longer than "
"this, it is cropped.  If it is shorter than this, it is padded with "
"zeros.  If `n` is not given, it is determined from the length of the "
"input along the axis specified by `axis`."
msgstr ""
"输出变换轴的长度。对于 `n` 个输出点，需要 ``n//2 + 1`` 个输入点。如果输入"
"比这长，则会被裁剪；如果比这短，则会用零填充。如果未给出 `n`，则根据 `"
"axis` 指定轴上的输入长度确定。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.hfft.hfft:12 of
msgid "Axis over which to compute the FFT. If not given, the last axis is used."
msgstr "计算 FFT 的轴。如果未给出，则使用最后一个轴。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.hfft.hfft:15 of
msgid "Normalization mode (see `mt.fft`). Default is None."
msgstr "归一化模式（参见 `mt.fft`）。默认为 None。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.hfft.hfft of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.hfft.hfft:18 of
msgid ""
"**out** -- The truncated or zero-padded input, transformed along the axis"
" indicated by `axis`, or the last one if `axis` is not specified. The "
"length of the transformed axis is `n`, or, if `n` is not given, ``2*m - "
"2`` where ``m`` is the length of the transformed axis of the input. To "
"get an odd number of output points, `n` must be specified, for instance "
"as ``2*m - 1`` in the typical case,"
msgstr ""
"**out** -- 被截断或零填充的输入，沿 `axis` 指定的轴进行变换，如果未指定 `"
"axis` 则使用最后一个轴。变换轴的长度为 `n`，如果未给出 `n`，则为 ``2*m - "
"2``，其中 ``m`` 是输入变换轴的长度。要获得奇数个输出点，必须指定 `n`，"
"例如典型情况下为 ``2*m - 1``。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.hfft.hfft of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.hfft.hfft of
msgid "抛出"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.hfft.hfft:26 of
msgid "If `axis` is larger than the last axis of `a`."
msgstr "如果 `axis` 大于 `a` 的最后一个轴。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.hfft.hfft:30 of
msgid ":py:obj:`rfft`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.hfft.hfft:31 of
msgid "Compute the one-dimensional FFT for real input."
msgstr "计算实数输入的一维 FFT。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.hfft.hfft:33 of
msgid ":py:obj:`ihfft`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.hfft.hfft:34 of
msgid "The inverse of `hfft`."
msgstr "`hfft` 的逆变换。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.hfft.hfft:37 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.hfft.hfft:38 of
msgid ""
"`hfft`/`ihfft` are a pair analogous to `rfft`/`irfft`, but for the "
"opposite case: here the signal has Hermitian symmetry in the time domain "
"and is real in the frequency domain. So here it's `hfft` for which you "
"must supply the length of the result if it is to be odd."
msgstr ""
"`hfft`/`ihfft` 是与 `rfft`/`irfft` 相似的成对函数，但用于相反的情况：这里"
"的信号在时域中具有 Hermitian 对称性，在频域中是实数。因此，如果要得到奇数"
"长度的结果，必须为 `hfft` 提供结果长度。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.hfft.hfft:43 of
msgid "even: ``ihfft(hfft(a, 2*len(a) - 2) == a``, within roundoff error,"
msgstr "偶数情况：``ihfft(hfft(a, 2*len(a) - 2) == a``，在舍入误差范围内，"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.hfft.hfft:44 of
msgid "odd: ``ihfft(hfft(a, 2*len(a) - 1) == a``, within roundoff error."
msgstr "奇数情况：``ihfft(hfft(a, 2*len(a) - 1) == a``，在舍入误差范围内。"

